nhc_headline: ...TROPICAL STORM CONDITIONS POSSIBLE FOR PARTS OF BAJA CALIFORNIA SUR AS LIFE-THREATENING SURF AFFECTS THIS AREA AND MUCH OF WEST-CENTRAL MEXICO...
summary: ...TROPICAL STORM CONDITIONS POSSIBLE FOR PARTS OF BAJA CALIFORNIA SUR AS LIFE-THREATENING SURF AFFECTS THIS AREA AND MUCH OF WEST-CENTRAL MEXICO... As of 5:00 PM MST Tue Oct 07 the center of Priscilla was located near 20.3, -111.2 with movement NW at 9 mph. The minimum central pressure was 958 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 110 mph.
